div.h3: Data Walk: From Firmware Tables to Frame Allocator Bitmap

div.p: Frame Index = Physical Address / 4096 Bitmap Word = Frame Index / 32 Bit Position = Frame Index % 32
// Mark frame as used bitmap[word] |= (1 << bit)
// Mark frame as free bitmap[word] &= ~(1 << bit)
4GB system: 1,048,576 frames Bitmap size: 128 KB (32,768 words)
